<p style="text-align: justify;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-1529" href="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/?attachment_id=1529"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1529" title="6288602745_7b2ffc96b1" src="http://www.faitsetcauses.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/6288602745_7b2ffc96b1-300x240.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="240" /></a></p>
